WEBVTT

01:37.070 --> 01:40.990
[The Best Thing]

01:41.330 --> 01:48.479
[Agarwood]
[Episode 10]
[Pungent, bitter, mild]
[Helps breathe, reduces pain, stops vomiting, relieves cough]

01:51.560 --> 01:52.150
Come and take a look.

01:52.150 --> 01:54.070
This is the greenhouse,

01:56.090 --> 01:57.890
ahead of which is the farm.

01:58.360 --> 02:01.080
When we were at college,

02:01.100 --> 02:02.420
we usually came here to do research.

02:02.450 --> 02:04.120
The air here is so fresh.

02:04.150 --> 02:05.070
This greenhouse

02:05.070 --> 02:05.840
is where we introduce,

02:05.840 --> 02:08.080
protect and cultivate endangered medicinal plants.

02:08.680 --> 02:10.120
For example, dendrobium candidum like this

02:10.500 --> 02:12.430
brings great benefits to the stomach and cardiovascular system.

02:12.770 --> 02:14.890
It also helps to suppress tumor growth.

02:15.760 --> 02:16.800
But in the past,

02:16.800 --> 02:18.850
wild dendrobium candidum was scarce

02:18.850 --> 02:19.970
and very precious.

02:20.520 --> 02:21.410
It would be a shame

02:21.410 --> 02:22.470
if patients couldn't have access

02:22.500 --> 02:23.500
to such a good medicinal material.

02:24.410 --> 02:25.970
With the nowadays improved greenhouse technology,

02:26.000 --> 02:28.040
high-quality dendrobium candidum can be put into mass production.

02:28.730 --> 02:31.600
It is a great ingredient for tea or cooking in daily life.

02:33.730 --> 02:35.520
Do we get to use it this time?

02:35.770 --> 02:36.520
Sure.

02:36.800 --> 02:37.970
It is a nice choice to make tea

02:37.970 --> 02:39.480
with dendrobium candidum.

02:50.690 --> 02:52.640
Look how tall it has grown.

02:53.320 --> 02:54.010
Do you remember what this is?

02:54.010 --> 02:54.850
The leaves have withered.

02:54.850 --> 02:55.450
The leaves....

02:56.570 --> 02:58.290
With jagged edges.

03:01.450 --> 03:02.520
Five-flavor fruit?

03:03.760 --> 03:05.550
Dry these leaves

03:05.640 --> 03:07.170
in the sun,

03:07.170 --> 03:09.010
and they can be used as a traditional Chinese herbal medicine.

03:09.010 --> 03:10.600
Did you plant all of this?

03:10.600 --> 03:11.690
Can I pluck some?

03:12.250 --> 03:12.850
Yes.

03:14.250 --> 03:15.040
It wasn't that hard.

03:21.450 --> 03:22.600
Xiangya, Senior Lin,

03:23.570 --> 03:24.520
have a taste of this.

03:24.930 --> 03:25.800
It's delicious.

03:25.850 --> 03:27.170
It tastes sweet and sour.

03:27.950 --> 03:28.780
What is this?

03:28.970 --> 03:29.570
Five-flavor fruit.

03:30.360 --> 03:31.520
We don't need to wash it first?

03:33.200 --> 03:33.690
It's okay.

03:34.130 --> 03:35.000
Let them try it.

03:38.670 --> 03:40.060
It looks dainty.

03:40.079 --> 03:40.690
Isn't it?

03:52.780 --> 03:54.060
Shen Xifan!

03:55.410 --> 03:56.040
You tricked us,

03:56.170 --> 03:56.800
didn't you?

03:56.800 --> 03:57.079
Xifan!

03:57.079 --> 03:57.850
You tricked us!

03:57.850 --> 03:58.290
Whoa!

03:58.290 --> 03:58.800
Come back here!

03:58.800 --> 03:59.730
Come on, try it.

03:59.730 --> 04:00.200
Give it a try.

04:00.200 --> 04:01.570
We're good.

04:01.570 --> 04:04.520
Give it a try!

04:04.520 --> 04:05.720
Come on!

04:05.750 --> 04:06.170
Take a bite.

04:06.170 --> 04:07.010
No, no.

04:07.010 --> 04:08.890
Just eat it! Come on.

04:10.130 --> 04:11.010
Come on!

04:11.010 --> 04:11.890
You eat it.

04:18.519 --> 04:22.150
[Hang City Traditional Chinese Medicine Herbal Farm]

04:30.320 --> 04:32.100
Shen Xifan, good for you.

04:32.190 --> 04:33.750
You took traditional Chinese medicine twice,

04:33.770 --> 04:35.210
and now you've learned to prank me with it.

04:36.080 --> 04:37.010
I'll take that as a compliment.

04:46.250 --> 04:47.680
It tastes good.

04:47.890 --> 04:48.690
What is it?

04:48.890 --> 04:50.250
It consists of five-flavor fruit.

04:50.250 --> 04:51.370
We added some honey to it,

04:51.370 --> 04:52.570
so it tastes better.

04:54.960 --> 04:57.990
Is it a kind of drink that doctors like you usually fix for yourselves?

05:00.600 --> 05:01.600
Not really.

05:02.120 --> 05:03.440
I prefer coke.

05:03.890 --> 05:05.570
You're pretty funny, handsome.

05:05.570 --> 05:07.690
How come I never noticed it?

05:13.370 --> 05:15.130
Li Jie, where is Dr. He?

05:15.130 --> 05:16.760
Why don't you go find him?

05:18.450 --> 05:19.520
I'll go find Dr. He.

05:29.670 --> 05:32.060
These medicinal herbs are products of the plantation.

05:32.080 --> 05:34.250
I've brought those that are commonly used for medicinal cuisine

05:34.250 --> 05:35.200
and aromatherapy.

05:37.320 --> 05:39.610
TCM is particular about the specific health-keeping tactics in each season,

05:39.610 --> 05:41.159
so we would choose different regimens

05:41.159 --> 05:41.960
according to seasonal changes

05:41.960 --> 05:43.720
and the 24 solar terms.

05:44.500 --> 05:46.370
Now, our goal here

05:46.390 --> 05:48.560
is to nourish kidneys and increase moisture in the human body.

05:48.790 --> 05:50.390
The recipes tend to be mild.

05:52.130 --> 05:53.450
That being said,

05:53.450 --> 05:55.450
considering the elderly's health conditions,

05:55.840 --> 05:58.520
I suggest you differentiate the effects

05:59.010 --> 05:59.960
and choose appropriate recipes

05:59.960 --> 06:01.450
for different individuals.

06:01.890 --> 06:03.050
How do we do that?

06:04.080 --> 06:06.690
The medicinal cuisine here has five effects.

06:07.010 --> 06:07.960
It is good for sleep,

06:07.960 --> 06:09.570
the circulation of energy and blood, and kidneys.

06:10.010 --> 06:11.720
It also helps to clear fat, lower blood pressure and reduce dryness.

06:11.960 --> 06:12.760
It smells amazing.

06:12.760 --> 06:13.490
Here are the recipes.

06:13.490 --> 06:15.200
Pass them around and read them.

06:15.200 --> 06:15.930
Okay.

06:18.250 --> 06:18.720
Here you are.

06:21.050 --> 06:23.050
You can also create new recipes on your own.

06:23.050 --> 06:24.160
We will provide you with proper information

06:24.160 --> 06:25.610
and suggestions about different herbs.

06:25.810 --> 06:26.370
Thank you for all the hard work.

06:26.370 --> 06:27.030
You're welcome.

06:31.160 --> 06:32.159
There is boiled water outside.

06:32.159 --> 06:33.200
If you're interested,

06:33.200 --> 06:34.720
make some tea and have a taste.

06:35.250 --> 06:35.810
Okay.

06:35.810 --> 06:37.430
Can we make tea with these?

06:37.520 --> 06:38.930
Yeah, sure.

06:48.520 --> 06:50.200
These are dried lily bulbs.

06:50.960 --> 06:51.890
They reinforce lungs, relieve cough

06:51.890 --> 06:53.200
and soothe nerves.

06:54.570 --> 06:56.840
Then they're a good ingredient for medicinal cuisine in autumn.

06:58.200 --> 06:59.890
I've seen porridge with lily bulbs and lotus seeds being sold in supermarkets.

06:59.890 --> 07:01.690
This combination is a safe and convenient option, right?

07:04.450 --> 07:05.520
It being commonly seen

07:05.520 --> 07:07.200
means it is not special at all.

07:07.920 --> 07:08.810
We're not going for that option now.

07:11.110 --> 07:13.820
Many classic recipes involve lily bulbs.

07:13.840 --> 07:15.840
If we don't use lily bulbs,

07:16.120 --> 07:17.810
our workload might get too heavy.

07:19.620 --> 07:20.580
Cutie pie,

07:20.720 --> 07:22.010
why don't we befriend each other on Wechat?

07:22.010 --> 07:24.450
Maybe you can answer my questions if I have any.

07:28.960 --> 07:29.370
Sure.

07:31.280 --> 07:32.130
Let me scan your code.

07:42.370 --> 07:43.010
Done.

08:02.640 --> 08:04.130
What are you doing here alone?

08:05.930 --> 08:07.680
They're all studying medicinal cuisine.

08:07.810 --> 08:10.010
I'd like to find out what I can use for aromatherapy.

08:10.010 --> 08:11.160
We can save some time in this way.

08:12.640 --> 08:14.930
Which would you like to make, incense or sachets?

08:17.130 --> 08:18.130
Sachets.

08:18.130 --> 08:19.490
It's more convenient when I send them to the elderly.

08:19.490 --> 08:21.250
They can hang the sachets at the bedside.

08:21.300 --> 08:22.540
What's your recommendation?

08:24.280 --> 08:25.960
All of these are incense ingredients.

08:26.760 --> 08:27.660
Patchouli.

08:28.050 --> 08:28.930
Agarwood.

08:28.930 --> 08:29.930
Nutmeg.

08:29.930 --> 08:30.620
Sandalwood.

08:30.810 --> 08:31.610
Clove.

08:31.610 --> 08:32.520
And that is...

08:32.520 --> 08:33.490
Cinnamon.

08:33.490 --> 08:35.400
I know it's often used to make mulled wine.

08:36.130 --> 08:37.130
That is actually cassia.

08:37.760 --> 08:38.730
Cassia?

08:42.090 --> 08:44.440
What's the difference between cassia and cinnamon?

08:44.890 --> 08:47.090
Cinnamon seems to be more often used abroad.

08:47.970 --> 08:48.800
It's not about that.

08:49.520 --> 08:51.280
Cinnamon derives from the bark of the Cinnamomum verum tree,

08:51.280 --> 08:52.280
whereas cassia

08:52.280 --> 08:54.160
is sourced from the bark of the Cinnamomum cassia tree.

08:54.920 --> 08:57.340
Cassia is spicier

08:57.520 --> 09:00.440
while cinnamon is lighter and softer.

09:01.440 --> 09:03.130
So, cassia is often used for cooking,

09:03.130 --> 09:04.890
and cinnamon for aromatherapy.

09:06.370 --> 09:08.920
It's no wonder that many perfumes contain cinnamon.

09:25.370 --> 09:27.090
Let's go somewhere else.

09:30.280 --> 09:31.370
Where to?

09:31.980 --> 09:33.860
A place with more materials for aromatherapy.

09:39.680 --> 09:40.440
Let's go.

09:41.970 --> 09:42.640
Come on.

09:51.800 --> 09:52.330
Here it is.

09:56.130 --> 09:57.010
This is

09:57.010 --> 09:58.250
an agarwood tree.

09:59.280 --> 10:00.250
The resin formed

10:00.250 --> 10:01.490
and cut off from these places

10:01.490 --> 10:02.610
is what we call agarwood.

10:04.850 --> 10:05.630
Sniff it.

10:10.520 --> 10:12.010
It does smell nice.

10:12.920 --> 10:14.330
It gives out...

10:15.730 --> 10:17.130
a very familiar scent.

10:18.560 --> 10:19.330
Familiar?

10:21.040 --> 10:21.970
Like the perfume you wear?

10:23.680 --> 10:24.490
No.

10:27.400 --> 10:28.400
It smells like you.

10:29.850 --> 10:30.800
Me?

10:32.640 --> 10:34.040
I don't wear perfume.

11:12.520 --> 11:14.040
The scent is gone.

11:17.890 --> 11:18.990
As I said,

11:19.160 --> 11:20.400
I never wear perfume.

11:23.850 --> 11:25.370
Then maybe one day,

11:25.370 --> 11:27.450
the scent of agarwood got on you,

11:27.640 --> 11:29.010
and I just happened to be around.

11:30.250 --> 11:32.130
Or perhaps,

11:32.320 --> 11:33.400
this scent

11:33.890 --> 11:34.730
resembles you.

11:35.280 --> 11:36.040
It resembles me?

11:36.640 --> 11:37.520
In what way?

11:39.400 --> 11:42.490
It is very gentle and mild.

11:42.490 --> 11:44.330
It smells pleasant and not bland at all.

11:45.890 --> 11:48.110
So this is what you think of me.

11:51.730 --> 11:53.370
An agarwood tree without resin

11:53.370 --> 11:54.900
is just an ordinary piece of timber.

11:55.400 --> 11:57.680
But once it forms resin, it becomes true agarwood,

11:58.160 --> 12:01.220
and a top-grade medicinal material that helps with the circulation of energy.

12:02.730 --> 12:04.970
You think highly of me.

12:10.130 --> 12:12.210
I shouldn't have said that sentence.

12:12.890 --> 12:13.560
Don't worry about that.

12:13.950 --> 12:16.000
I've received all your compliments.

12:17.970 --> 12:19.250
It has come to my notice

12:19.680 --> 12:22.280
that you do have a lot in common with this scent.

12:23.330 --> 12:25.640
It is a complicated kind of smell,

12:26.040 --> 12:27.160
somewhat like

12:28.280 --> 12:29.850
a toxic substance.

12:32.400 --> 12:33.640
Is it the smell of garbage?

12:37.250 --> 12:38.730
You got drunk that night

12:38.730 --> 12:40.040
and called me garbage.

12:40.760 --> 12:42.250
You know I was drunk.

12:42.250 --> 12:43.760
What I said was nonsense.

12:43.760 --> 12:45.400
People tell the truth when they're drunk.

12:45.400 --> 12:46.250
Suppose I did tell the truth,

12:46.250 --> 12:47.490
that might not be directed at you.

12:47.490 --> 12:48.540
Not me, indeed.

12:48.730 --> 12:50.370
I am a top-grade medicine that helps with energy circulation.

12:54.860 --> 12:56.950
For frustrated and depressed people

12:56.980 --> 12:58.530
like you,

12:58.560 --> 13:00.050
I am the best cure.

13:00.890 --> 13:01.970
You're talking nonsense.

13:02.490 --> 13:03.800
The prescription you made for me

13:03.840 --> 13:04.960
does not include agarwood.

13:09.470 --> 13:10.580
Someday it will.

13:30.250 --> 13:32.040
What are you going to do with that toy?

13:33.080 --> 13:34.560
You should dispose of it.

13:34.580 --> 13:35.550
I won't play with it anyway.

13:35.990 --> 13:36.560
Okay.

13:37.340 --> 13:38.380
Well,

13:38.800 --> 13:40.410
thank you. I said that for my son.

13:45.940 --> 13:46.540
Let's go.

13:49.820 --> 13:50.690
Okay.

14:00.010 --> 14:01.280
When we get back,

14:01.680 --> 14:02.870
I'll give you a present.

14:05.930 --> 14:07.220
What is it?

14:10.520 --> 14:11.640
You'll know when we're back.

14:44.370 --> 14:45.760
I've arrived at your department building.

14:56.610 --> 14:57.330
Coming right up.

15:03.110 --> 15:04.710
The photo has been edited. Send it to Dr. He.

15:08.370 --> 15:10.640
You could've sent it to him yourself.

15:14.160 --> 15:15.130
I'm asking you to do it.

15:44.210 --> 15:45.040
Sorry for the long wait.

15:46.170 --> 15:47.780
No worries. It wasn't that long.

15:58.050 --> 15:59.750
What's up? Why are you smiling?

16:00.950 --> 16:01.910
I'm thinking

16:02.370 --> 16:03.250
that this is the exact place

16:03.250 --> 16:04.250
where you sat

16:04.250 --> 16:05.850
and cursed me that night.

16:06.730 --> 16:08.610
I was drunk at that time, wasn't I?

16:08.610 --> 16:10.160
-Sorry.
-I'm just kidding.

16:10.850 --> 16:11.400
Here,

16:12.160 --> 16:13.610
I made you a sachet.

16:14.040 --> 16:14.800
Thank you.

16:14.800 --> 16:15.400
Take a sniff.

16:18.610 --> 16:19.560
I smell agarwood.

16:20.210 --> 16:21.290
You have a keen nose.

16:24.340 --> 16:24.930
By the way,

16:26.160 --> 16:27.400
you didn't show up for a follow-up visit yesterday.

16:27.490 --> 16:28.700
What about next week's medicine?

16:29.680 --> 16:31.490
Oh, I'm feeling much better.

16:31.490 --> 16:33.280
Don't you think the medication can stop now?

16:34.560 --> 16:35.280
Okay.

16:35.560 --> 16:37.560
Come over for moxibustion when you have time.

16:38.790 --> 16:39.460
What now?

16:39.490 --> 16:41.370
Do you mean I can't come meet you unless I'm sick?

16:56.490 --> 16:58.640
No, you can come and dine with me.

16:59.440 --> 17:00.170
It's up to you.

17:06.750 --> 17:07.710
Well,

17:09.089 --> 17:10.290
I'll see about that later.

17:36.830 --> 17:37.500
You're back.

17:37.810 --> 17:38.440
Yeah.

17:39.330 --> 17:40.530
Good timing.

17:45.960 --> 17:47.050
What's that?

17:48.090 --> 17:48.850
A gift from the clinic.

17:48.850 --> 17:49.610
Come on, take a sniff.

17:50.900 --> 17:51.450
It smells nice.

17:51.470 --> 17:52.270
It does, right?

17:58.100 --> 18:00.730
Don't you think you're overjoyed at a free sachet?

18:01.770 --> 18:02.530
Am I?

18:03.240 --> 18:03.930
I doubt it.

18:05.640 --> 18:06.770
I'll go change.

18:10.570 --> 18:12.160
That sachet from the clinic

18:12.160 --> 18:13.240
has a scent of agarwood.

18:13.240 --> 18:14.200
It smells quite nice.

18:14.200 --> 18:14.920
Shall we go get one too?

18:14.920 --> 18:15.680
Sure. Sure. Sure.

18:17.090 --> 18:17.870
Today...

18:19.440 --> 18:20.480
No beer for today, again.

18:29.960 --> 18:33.340
♫A faint aroma♫

18:35.860 --> 18:40.490
♫Slowly awakening my heart♫

18:36.850 --> 18:38.890
For frustrated and depressed people

18:38.890 --> 18:40.440
like you,

18:40.440 --> 18:41.850
I am the best cure.

18:42.120 --> 18:46.840
♫The elusive little mist appears and disappears♫

18:42.770 --> 18:43.720
You're talking nonsense.

18:44.200 --> 18:45.440
The prescription you made for me

18:45.440 --> 18:46.570
does not include agarwood.

18:47.240 --> 18:54.090
♫Quietly entering your world, your memories♫

18:51.310 --> 18:52.480
Someday it will.

18:55.160 --> 18:58.360
♫The unexpected encounter with the wind♫

19:01.040 --> 19:05.180
♫Layer by layer, rendering the air♫

19:07.450 --> 19:11.680
♫The whispers that are sometimes far, sometimes near♫

19:12.490 --> 19:17.660
♫Exchanging our hidden secrets♫

19:17.610 --> 19:18.330
Hello?

19:18.330 --> 19:19.770
Uh, is your work finished?

19:19.690 --> 19:24.680
♫Using my breath♫

19:19.770 --> 19:20.920
Yes. It was just over.

19:21.920 --> 19:22.770
How is it going?

19:24.000 --> 19:24.920
What are you asking about?

19:25.720 --> 19:27.680
I mean things between you and Miss Shen.

19:25.900 --> 19:31.670
♫To blend the soothing scent of love♫

19:29.890 --> 19:30.720
Great, I think.

19:31.930 --> 19:34.430
♫To merge in♫

19:33.130 --> 19:35.400
Li Jie does have a good eye.

19:36.770 --> 19:37.610
Li Jie?

19:37.820 --> 19:40.930
♫Air♫

19:38.330 --> 19:39.480
What did he tell you?

19:40.530 --> 19:43.220
He said you and that girl exchanged amorous glances.

19:44.610 --> 19:45.780
What amorous glances?

19:44.960 --> 19:48.910
♫Shortens the distance between two hearts♫

19:45.810 --> 19:47.200
I didn't do that.

19:49.050 --> 19:49.770
I just...

19:50.980 --> 19:57.710
♫You're everywhere♫

19:51.400 --> 19:52.810
clicked with her.

19:54.400 --> 19:55.920
Alright, no more question.

19:59.620 --> 20:01.340
The elderly visiting group will arrive soon.

20:01.810 --> 20:03.200
Everyone, look sharp!

20:03.200 --> 20:04.000
-Yes.
-Yes.

20:07.000 --> 20:08.480
Alright, here it is!

20:08.610 --> 20:10.570
Hold onto your belongings and get off the coach nice and slow.

20:12.850 --> 20:13.290
Welcome.

20:13.290 --> 20:14.000
Nice to see you again.

20:14.720 --> 20:16.160
Easy, easy, easy.

20:16.720 --> 20:18.240
Follow the flag!

20:18.240 --> 20:19.240
Easy with your pace.

20:19.240 --> 20:20.440
Watch your step.

20:20.720 --> 20:21.400
Uncles and aunties, nice and slow.

20:21.400 --> 20:22.090
Nice and slow.

20:22.090 --> 20:23.240
Oh, how beautiful!

20:23.240 --> 20:24.200
Welcome.

20:25.050 --> 20:26.130
Nice and slow.

20:32.600 --> 20:33.410
Go check into the hotel.

20:33.430 --> 20:35.380
Bring your belongings and proceed to check-in.

20:35.410 --> 20:36.700
Nice and slow.

20:37.050 --> 20:38.810
Just go directly to check-in.

20:38.810 --> 20:40.160
Don't forget your belongings.

20:40.160 --> 20:41.130
Welcome.

20:43.820 --> 20:44.740
Slowly, ma'am.

20:44.810 --> 20:45.610
Welcome.

20:45.920 --> 20:46.720
Thank you.

20:51.090 --> 20:52.720
Okay. Please sign here.

20:52.720 --> 20:53.720
Hello, ma'am.

20:53.720 --> 20:54.610
You wanna check out, right?

20:55.160 --> 20:56.050
Get ready.

20:57.020 --> 20:58.610
Three, two, one.

20:59.420 --> 21:00.810
Cheese!

21:01.570 --> 21:02.440
Manager Shen,

21:02.440 --> 21:04.060
where can I get breakfast?

21:04.160 --> 21:05.330
I'm feeling a bit dizzy.

21:05.330 --> 21:06.330
I'll take you there.

21:06.330 --> 21:07.440
Breakfast will start in an hour.

21:07.440 --> 21:08.090
Okay, okay, okay.

21:08.090 --> 21:08.920
Come on, let's go.

21:08.920 --> 21:10.090
Hello, hello, hello.

21:10.090 --> 21:11.130
This way, please. This way.

21:13.810 --> 21:16.510
Three, two, one, cheese!

21:16.960 --> 21:17.810
Let's take one more photo.

21:19.970 --> 21:24.050
Three, two, one, cheese!

21:25.150 --> 21:26.650
[Yuncong All Day Dining Restaurant]

21:30.610 --> 21:31.680
Uncles and aunties,

21:31.680 --> 21:32.710
we've designed new dishes

21:32.730 --> 21:34.330
for the hotel restaurant.

21:34.330 --> 21:36.530
They're special in their own way. Please have a try.

21:36.800 --> 21:37.640
Manager Xu,

21:37.640 --> 21:39.000
all of these are traditional Chinese medicinal herbs.

21:39.000 --> 21:40.090
Good stuff!

21:40.090 --> 21:40.920
Yes, you're right.

21:40.920 --> 21:41.480
Uncles and aunties,

21:41.480 --> 21:42.530
let me give you a brief introduction.

21:42.530 --> 21:43.290
This is the area

21:43.290 --> 21:45.850
where we prepare medicinal cuisine.

21:45.850 --> 21:47.050
All the materials we use

21:47.050 --> 21:49.050
are the freshest seasonal herbs.

21:49.400 --> 21:50.160
Not bad, not bad.

21:50.160 --> 21:51.440
Is this donkey-hide gelatin?

21:51.440 --> 21:52.310
Uncles and aunties,

21:53.000 --> 21:55.770
here is some porridge made with red dates, white jelly mushroom and lotus seeds.

21:56.050 --> 21:57.090
It reduces dryness and is good for blood.

21:57.680 --> 21:58.470
This porridge is proper food

21:58.500 --> 21:59.610
for autumn days like these.

21:59.770 --> 22:01.050
Sounds good.

22:01.050 --> 22:02.610
Each of us should get one bowl later.

22:02.960 --> 22:04.330
Good. One bowl for each of us.

22:04.330 --> 22:04.850
Right.

22:04.850 --> 22:05.770
We gotta taste it.

22:05.770 --> 22:07.090
We've also prepared crucian carp soup.

22:07.530 --> 22:07.850
There is

22:07.850 --> 22:08.720
ginger, spring onions,

22:08.720 --> 22:09.420
astragalus

22:09.440 --> 22:10.160
and red dates.

22:10.680 --> 22:11.680
They help lower cholesterol levels.

22:11.680 --> 22:12.960
lower cholesterol levels?

22:12.960 --> 22:13.930
I want a bowl of this porridge too.

22:14.240 --> 22:14.920
Give me a bowl of it.

22:14.920 --> 22:16.050
A bowl of porridge, sir.

22:16.050 --> 22:16.770
Miss,

22:16.770 --> 22:19.010
is there a suitable drink for the elderly like us?

22:19.140 --> 22:20.140
In the past few days,

22:20.160 --> 22:22.040
we've been on planes and buses.

22:22.160 --> 22:24.050
We feel pain in the legs and knees.

22:24.050 --> 22:24.770
We're exhausted.

22:24.770 --> 22:27.440
We will serve some soup made with eucommia, chestnuts, and chicken feet tonight.

22:27.720 --> 22:28.850
It's good for the kidneys and spleen.

22:28.850 --> 22:29.920
Maybe you can give it a try.

22:30.630 --> 22:32.770
-It's perfect for you.
-I've never tasted it.

22:32.770 --> 22:33.920
But I'm like to give it a try.

22:35.960 --> 22:37.290
We've placed aromatic materials

22:37.290 --> 22:38.530
under your pillows as a sleep aid.

22:38.850 --> 22:40.570
If you don't like the smell,

22:40.570 --> 22:41.800
I'll change it for you at any time.

22:42.240 --> 22:42.610
Just contact me.

22:42.610 --> 22:44.000
Okay, thank you.

22:45.000 --> 22:46.160
Come this way to see your room.

22:46.160 --> 22:47.090
Mm, okay.

22:47.090 --> 22:48.050
This way, please.

22:49.370 --> 22:52.570
Hello. Since you just informed the reception of your sleeplessness,

22:52.570 --> 22:54.720
we've prepared a pillow filled with Chinese senna for you.

22:54.720 --> 22:56.060
It is good for your liver and eyes,

22:56.090 --> 22:57.380
and it also helps to calm your nerves.

22:57.640 --> 22:58.290
Please come in.

22:58.290 --> 22:59.010
Thank you.

23:13.570 --> 23:14.480
Hello!

23:15.400 --> 23:16.200
Hello.

23:16.610 --> 23:18.050
How may I help you?

23:19.130 --> 23:19.850
Well,

23:20.610 --> 23:22.610
could you change the aroma

23:22.610 --> 23:24.040
in my room?

23:24.090 --> 23:25.590
I don't like the smell of grass.

23:26.820 --> 23:27.700
I'm sorry.

23:29.570 --> 23:31.000
8252.

23:31.850 --> 23:33.960
Are you Ms. Liu Yunci?

23:34.480 --> 23:35.290
Yes, I am.

23:35.290 --> 23:36.010
Let me see.

23:37.090 --> 23:38.200
Before checking in,

23:38.200 --> 23:40.260
you didn't specify any special requirements.

23:40.280 --> 23:42.480
So we prepared an aroma of mugwort,

23:42.510 --> 23:44.970
sandalwood, magnolia, and camphor for you.

23:45.290 --> 23:45.870
This mainly

23:45.900 --> 23:48.180
inhibits bacterial activity and cleans the air.

23:48.780 --> 23:49.390
That said,

23:49.410 --> 23:51.160
it's fine if you don't like it.

23:51.160 --> 23:53.050
May I ask what efficacy do you wish

23:53.050 --> 23:54.810
the new aroma will bring?

23:54.810 --> 23:56.290
I don't care for the efficacy.

23:56.290 --> 23:59.520
I just want something mellow and warm.

23:59.770 --> 24:00.890
Let me see what I can get for you.

24:02.480 --> 24:04.850
Here is another type of aroma we offer.

24:04.850 --> 24:08.090
It smells agarwood, fragrant rosewood, fructus amomi and styrax benzoin.

24:08.090 --> 24:09.920
It mainly improves blood circulation and relieves pain.

24:09.920 --> 24:10.850
Do you like it?

24:11.040 --> 24:11.960
It relieves pain...

24:13.000 --> 24:14.370
I'd like to give it a try.

24:14.920 --> 24:15.680
Okay, no problem.

24:15.680 --> 24:16.720
I'll bring it to you right away.

24:17.610 --> 24:18.570
Okay, thank you.

24:18.570 --> 24:19.270
You're welcome.

24:21.770 --> 24:23.890
Housekeeping Dept., agarwood aroma for Room 8252.

24:23.890 --> 24:25.050
Please send the supplies up here now.

24:33.240 --> 24:34.000
Congratulations.

24:34.440 --> 24:35.810
You've completed another session of chemotherapy.

24:36.570 --> 24:37.720
Are you feeling any discomfort?

24:38.160 --> 24:39.000
I'm not having diarrhea

24:39.000 --> 24:40.000
or vomitting.

24:40.610 --> 24:41.960
But I do have a lot of burps.

24:42.800 --> 24:44.030
Those are not burps.

24:44.060 --> 24:44.910
They're hiccups

24:45.540 --> 24:47.830
caused by the stomach injury induced by the chemotherapy.

24:49.370 --> 24:50.480
Starting from tonight,

24:50.480 --> 24:52.480
you need to take some stomach medicine

24:52.480 --> 24:54.000
and have millet porridge, et cetera.

24:54.000 --> 24:54.920
You will soon feel better.

24:56.480 --> 24:58.290
That's great. Thank you, Dr. He.

24:58.290 --> 24:59.720
You care a lot about Ze.

25:00.160 --> 25:01.330
I'm just doing my job.

25:03.680 --> 25:04.200
Oh, right.

25:06.260 --> 25:07.540
A lady has sent you a present

25:07.560 --> 25:09.450
to reward your positive attitude towards receiving treatment.

25:10.090 --> 25:10.370
Take it.

25:10.370 --> 25:11.290
This is too much.

25:11.290 --> 25:12.530
It's alright. Just keep it.

25:13.970 --> 25:15.530
As long as Ze continues the treatment, takes it seriously,

25:15.550 --> 25:16.370
and recovers soon,

25:16.370 --> 25:17.680
that lady will be very pleased.

25:21.050 --> 25:21.850
Just take it.

25:26.370 --> 25:27.240
Take it out. Have a look.

25:29.810 --> 25:30.400
What do you think?

25:30.810 --> 25:31.500
Do you like it?

25:54.480 --> 25:56.200
What a huge Transformer!

25:56.200 --> 25:56.770
Mom, I've never received

25:56.770 --> 25:58.050
a Transformer as big as this one.

25:59.330 --> 26:00.820
Be gentle with it. Don't break it.

26:03.610 --> 26:06.030
Dr. He, who is this kind lady?

26:06.320 --> 26:07.800
I must thank her in person.

26:07.820 --> 26:09.240
It's such an expensive toy.

26:09.510 --> 26:10.330
No worries.

26:10.890 --> 26:12.050
I'll tell her about your gratitude.

26:14.090 --> 26:14.890
She...

26:16.200 --> 26:17.570
She's just a friend of mine.

26:17.920 --> 26:18.680
She heard about what happened

26:18.680 --> 26:19.640
to you and Zhao Ze by chance,

26:19.640 --> 26:21.090
and was impressed by your toughness,

26:21.090 --> 26:22.440
so she'd like to give Ze a present.

26:25.370 --> 26:26.290
Let's keep up the good work.

26:26.290 --> 26:27.530
Perhaps you can be discharged before Chinese New Year.

26:31.880 --> 26:32.880
Thank you, Dr. He.

26:33.290 --> 26:34.440
Tell your friend I appreciate her kindness.

26:34.480 --> 26:35.710
You're welcome.

26:40.680 --> 26:42.480
May I take a photo of you

26:42.510 --> 26:43.580
and send it to her?

26:44.400 --> 26:46.770
Then she'll know her best wishes have reached you.

26:46.770 --> 26:47.480
Okay.

26:48.460 --> 26:49.980
Can I take the photo with Mom?

26:50.530 --> 26:52.160
Sure thing.

26:53.130 --> 26:54.330
Wait, let me put on a hat.

26:56.240 --> 26:56.770
Alright,

26:57.330 --> 26:58.000
look at the camera.

26:58.400 --> 26:59.130
Three,

26:59.130 --> 26:59.890
two,

26:59.890 --> 27:00.220
one.

27:00.240 --> 27:00.750
Smile!

27:01.160 --> 27:01.960
Let's take one more.

27:02.890 --> 27:03.670
Three,

27:03.920 --> 27:04.720
two,

27:04.720 --> 27:05.290
one.

27:07.440 --> 27:08.160
Done.

27:08.380 --> 27:09.340
What a nice photo.

27:11.590 --> 27:12.910
It can be opened up.

27:13.890 --> 27:14.720
This...

27:15.680 --> 27:16.680
This wheel.

27:17.050 --> 27:18.480
You're very smart.

27:20.440 --> 27:21.400
This wheel...

27:41.370 --> 27:42.640
Your gift has been delivered.

27:43.240 --> 27:44.290
The kid loves it.

27:44.720 --> 27:45.810
He asked me to thank you on his behalf.

27:50.530 --> 27:52.850
Glad he received it. I was worried that you might keep it for yourself

27:52.850 --> 27:54.050
and play with it at home.

28:13.440 --> 28:16.050
The kid looks spirited.

28:16.570 --> 28:17.850
Will he be discharged soon?

28:22.780 --> 28:24.050
He is diagnosed with pediatric leukemia,

28:24.050 --> 28:25.490
and has just finished a session of chemotherapy.

28:25.560 --> 28:27.750
I hope he will get well enough to be discharged before Chinese New Year.

28:33.050 --> 28:35.090
Then I wish him to be healthy

28:35.090 --> 28:36.810
and even stronger than the Transformer.

28:41.040 --> 28:43.430
If you had come here that day,

28:43.530 --> 28:45.090
you could've given him your best regards in person.

29:13.000 --> 29:14.960
The kind lady wishes you to be healthy

29:15.440 --> 29:17.680
and grow stronger than the Transformer.

29:19.400 --> 29:21.290
Please tell her I say "thank you."

29:22.290 --> 29:23.290
It's very courteous of you.

29:24.050 --> 29:25.440
I got it. See you around.

29:30.640 --> 29:31.440
Senior He.

29:32.000 --> 29:32.630
Suye.

29:41.410 --> 29:43.720
Suye looks cheerful.

29:44.440 --> 29:45.640
That's rare.

29:47.850 --> 29:48.640
Huh? What?

29:49.450 --> 29:50.420
You're so silly.

29:51.090 --> 29:52.200
Isn't it obvious?

29:52.810 --> 29:53.960
Look at him.

29:53.960 --> 29:56.240
He must be texting Manager Shen.

29:56.890 --> 29:58.680
Have you ever seen him smile like this before?

30:01.570 --> 30:03.090
Last time when he smiled like this,

30:03.640 --> 30:05.130
he was still a college student.

30:05.920 --> 30:06.890
At that time, I...

30:07.300 --> 30:08.950
I was either in elementary or middle school.

30:08.970 --> 30:09.890
I can't recall.

30:10.200 --> 30:11.770
Anyway, it was many years ago.

30:13.770 --> 30:14.810
This is fun.

30:16.810 --> 30:18.130
When he was a college student...

30:43.720 --> 30:44.980
I'd like to ask you a question.

30:45.400 --> 30:45.930
Have a seat.

30:53.720 --> 30:54.390
What question?

30:55.000 --> 30:56.000
This has been on my mind for a long time.

30:56.770 --> 30:58.440
I think it's time I asked you.

31:01.270 --> 31:03.320
About the lady who sent me the Transformer,

31:03.770 --> 31:04.570
what does she mean to you?

31:12.610 --> 31:13.200
Just a friend?

31:13.920 --> 31:14.530
I don't think so.

31:15.960 --> 31:17.570
Is she your girlfriend or what?

31:20.200 --> 31:21.940
Aren't you a clever little boy?

31:22.200 --> 31:23.440
I can't believe I guessed it right.

31:25.160 --> 31:26.570
My plan is a failure now.

31:27.260 --> 31:28.020
What plan?

31:29.400 --> 31:30.640
A plan to find myself a father

31:31.610 --> 31:33.440
with my own efforts.

31:36.960 --> 31:37.640
Father?

31:40.850 --> 31:42.370
You seem like a decent guy to me.

31:43.250 --> 31:44.140
You treat me nicely.

31:45.000 --> 31:46.230
You treat my mom nicely too.

31:49.850 --> 31:51.000
I am your doctor.

31:51.000 --> 31:52.330
You are my patient.

31:52.330 --> 31:53.610
Certainly, I need to be nice to you,

31:54.370 --> 31:55.090
take good care of you,

31:55.090 --> 31:55.810
and help you recover.

31:55.810 --> 31:57.090
It is my responsibility to do so.

31:57.920 --> 31:59.480
When my father was alive,

32:00.050 --> 32:01.090
he always abused my mom

32:01.720 --> 32:02.570
and yelled at her.

32:04.530 --> 32:06.290
No one has talked to her as gently as you do.

32:07.690 --> 32:09.010
Mom has suffered a lot

32:09.870 --> 32:11.000
to get me medical treatment.

32:12.240 --> 32:13.720
I want to find her a man that will treat her right.

32:17.960 --> 32:19.480
But I can't be your father.

32:20.130 --> 32:20.890
Forget it.

32:21.570 --> 32:22.850
You have a girlfriend now.

32:23.400 --> 32:24.440
I might as well give up my plan.

32:24.920 --> 32:27.290
I've accepted her present after all.

32:28.680 --> 32:30.050
I wish you and that kind lady happiness.

32:32.370 --> 32:34.730
Message received.

32:36.370 --> 32:37.510
Come on, let me walk you back.

32:40.660 --> 32:42.090
We're finally getting a break.

32:42.480 --> 32:44.610
When the elderly visitors come back from the scenic spots,

32:44.610 --> 32:45.370
we'll be busy again.

32:45.640 --> 32:47.480
You're drinking hot bubble tea now.

32:48.090 --> 32:50.370
The weather is getting cooler. You should quit cold drinks too.

32:50.570 --> 32:52.370
I'm fine. The cold doesn't bother me.

32:53.370 --> 32:54.330
If you say so.

32:54.330 --> 32:55.290
Without Xiangya,

32:55.290 --> 32:56.730
I can't think of snarky words to say about you.

33:05.370 --> 33:07.890
I'll probably resign next year.

33:09.920 --> 33:11.610
You know my family runs a small company, right?

33:11.610 --> 33:13.960
My parents want to retire and have me take it over.

33:15.400 --> 33:16.850
So they can travel the world.

33:18.850 --> 33:20.240
Where does that sudden thought come from?

33:21.850 --> 33:24.810
They did talk to me about it some time ago,

33:24.810 --> 33:26.000
but I could never make up my mind.

33:26.000 --> 33:27.050
That's why I didn't tell you guys.

33:30.850 --> 33:32.000
Is Xiangya not aware of it?

33:34.370 --> 33:36.770
She overheard me and my mom talking on the phone.

33:39.640 --> 33:40.920
That explains

33:41.530 --> 33:43.130
why she was upset that day.

33:47.390 --> 33:47.980
I'm just wondering

33:48.000 --> 33:49.520
if she was upset

33:50.400 --> 33:52.770
because I am not that good a friend

33:53.090 --> 33:54.400
or what.

33:54.400 --> 33:55.760
Why don't I ask her for you?

33:55.890 --> 33:56.640
Please don't.

33:59.200 --> 34:00.960
She's interested

34:01.850 --> 34:03.540
in that young man now, isn't she?

34:04.560 --> 34:06.920
She is not really into Li Jie.

34:07.440 --> 34:08.520
You know how many

34:08.520 --> 34:11.080
younger boys pursued her in college,

34:11.080 --> 34:12.400
but she took interest in no one, right?

34:16.120 --> 34:18.000
Could it be possible

34:19.000 --> 34:20.770
that she likes younger men

34:20.770 --> 34:22.040
as she gets older now?

34:22.210 --> 34:23.520
You're the one getting old!

34:26.960 --> 34:27.730
I don't wanna

34:27.889 --> 34:28.600
talk about that now.

34:29.310 --> 34:30.199
Well,

34:34.170 --> 34:35.920
I have a question for you.

34:41.330 --> 34:43.199
Do you think I still stand a chance with her

34:44.080 --> 34:45.440
after being friends with her for such a long time?

35:12.040 --> 35:13.250
Please get a quiet room

35:13.250 --> 35:14.940
for the elder gentleman in Room 203.

35:15.080 --> 35:16.650
Remember, it must not be a room at the end of the hallway.

35:19.210 --> 35:20.950
Are you working late today?

35:24.800 --> 35:27.120
No. Why?

35:32.080 --> 35:34.000
The kid asked me to treat you to dinner

35:34.290 --> 35:35.600
so I could thank you for giving him a present.

35:39.290 --> 35:42.000
Okay. Will he join us?

35:47.230 --> 35:49.020
No. He has to stay in the hospital.

35:50.020 --> 35:51.100
Come to my place after work.

35:59.170 --> 36:00.590
His place again?

36:11.610 --> 36:13.810
Put on the slippers.

36:15.010 --> 36:15.700
Dinner will be ready soon.

36:15.720 --> 36:16.350
It'll just take a moment.

36:17.370 --> 36:19.080
There is freshly made five-flavor fruit tea on the table.

36:19.080 --> 36:20.150
Help yourself to it.

36:20.170 --> 36:20.780
Thank you.

36:52.560 --> 36:53.480
What's wrong?

36:55.290 --> 36:56.440
My arm is sore.

36:56.600 --> 36:58.920
I guess I pulled a muscle when I moved stuff.

36:59.400 --> 37:00.600
What did you move

37:00.600 --> 37:01.890
that could cause a muscle strain?

37:02.850 --> 37:03.600
A large number

37:03.600 --> 37:05.370
of elderly visitors are staying at my hotel, right?

37:05.370 --> 37:05.920
I'm telling you,

37:05.920 --> 37:07.520
these people are amazing.

37:07.850 --> 37:09.810
They buy local specialties,

37:09.810 --> 37:11.770
souvenirs from gift shops,

37:11.770 --> 37:13.370
and fruit from roadside stands.

37:13.920 --> 37:15.850
They are unbelievable.

37:15.850 --> 37:17.400
At 4 AM, they set out to watch the sunrise.

37:17.400 --> 37:19.330
When they come back in the afternoon, they are still energetic.

37:19.920 --> 37:21.920
They put us young people to shame.

37:21.920 --> 37:23.400
Now I can't take a few steps without panting.

37:24.690 --> 37:25.400
Nowadays,

37:25.770 --> 37:27.170
many elderly people

37:27.170 --> 37:28.770
know a lot about how to stay healthy.

37:29.210 --> 37:30.520
The elderly guests you're catering now

37:31.040 --> 37:32.560
are financially comfortable

37:32.810 --> 37:34.040
and healthy.

37:34.370 --> 37:35.290
Fragile young people like you

37:35.290 --> 37:36.690
who spend every day in air-conditioned offices

37:36.690 --> 37:38.730
with enormous stress

37:38.810 --> 37:39.770
are no match for them.

37:40.120 --> 37:42.690
Dr. He, you're so mean.

37:43.850 --> 37:45.560
How am I being mean?

37:46.370 --> 37:47.290
I'm just reminding you

37:47.290 --> 37:48.350
that you should take care

37:48.380 --> 37:50.050
of your body before making money.

37:51.000 --> 37:51.810
I got it.

37:51.810 --> 37:53.890
Everything you say is centered on your profession.

38:14.560 --> 38:15.520
Do you mind if I put pepper in this?

38:27.040 --> 38:27.900
Dr. He,

38:29.770 --> 38:30.890
this is...

38:36.650 --> 38:38.310
Dr. He, let me do you a favor.

38:38.920 --> 38:39.660
Check this out.

38:39.910 --> 38:41.110
Does it look like a ring to you?

38:43.290 --> 38:45.010
It's yours now. You're welcome.

38:49.070 --> 38:50.430
You gave me a ring in the afternoon,

38:51.130 --> 38:52.180
but I lost it.

38:52.690 --> 38:54.440
It went missing when I got off work.

38:55.110 --> 38:57.320
How about I buy you a new one?

38:59.890 --> 39:01.210
This is...
